@NODE note "Sad note...."

 I'm afraid that ArcExtract has come to an end for development, for the time
 being anyway.
 
 You might be wondering why, after all, I was updating it every few days.
 Well, the there are 2 reasons why.
 
 1. I don't really get enough support. So far, I have only received 3 EMails
 from people. This depresses me a little bit, because I'm sure there are
 more people using it.
 
 2. I'm getting a little bit tired and out of ideas to add to ArcExtract.
 This is one of the main reasons why I'm stopping development.
 
 
 I will from time to time update ArcExtract with a new Arc Type or 
 something, but not much else. If you want the situatuion to change, and you
 want me to continue development, please E-Mail me. If I get enough 
 responses, I will perhaps continue development.
 
 
                                                    Alvaro.
 
@ENDNODE 
 